    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "#  Hava Clinic - Daily AI FAQ Bot Digest\nAutomated infrastructure to monitor the AI patient assistant. \nExtracts daily metrics (Unanswered Queries, Medical Escalations, AI Errors, and Token Costs) and distributes formatted reports to stakeholders.\nRuns: Daily at 8:20 AM (Dubai Time)",
        "height": 208,
