      "id": "cf5fbdb6-8885-4605-b8f4-c84fa1054c34",
      "name": "Sticky Note"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 1. Database Extraction\nPulls the last 24 hours of telemetry data from the PostgreSQL database:\n• Escalated patient queries & medical risks\n• AI system crashes or errors\n• OpenAI/Anthropic Token Usage & API Cost Data",
        "height": 208,
        "width": 448
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        128,
        208
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "036e6e34-c7b9-4a62-8106-d6a2b947a381",
      "name": "Sticky Note1"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 2. Internal Operations Alert\nFormats the extracted AI metrics into a quick-read plain text digest. \nPushes immediately to the #all-grants Slack channel so the internal team can triage system errors and monitor daily API costs.",
        "height": 208,
        "width": 416,
        "color": 6
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        912,
        192
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "455385fe-c3d1-4afb-9c49-0bf7e4584884",
      "name": "Sticky Note2"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 3. Executive Email Generation\nProcesses the raw data into a responsive, branded HTML/CSS executive dashboard.\nHighlights critical Medical Risk escalations and daily AI financial spend for clinic management.",
